room_title: Escape room "Detention" by Lokey's Escape Rooms in Sarasota
room_description:
How did you get here? It’s all a blur. But here you are now. In front of a door. You press your ear against the cold metal. The door vibrates with power. You think you hear a cry for help. Your gut tells you to run away. But no – you have to do something.
You have to help whoever is on the other side of that door. No matter the consequences.
